===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|train|lang=fro||a delay", "a drawing out}}, from {{term|trainer||lang=fro|to pull out", "to draw}}, ultimately from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|traho|trahere|lang=la|to pull", "to draw}}. The verb was derived from the noun in Middle English.

